{"id":305236,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-黑龙江访民初东方逃脱地方监控继续北京/","date":"2013-07-24T01:19:24Z","modified":"2013-07-24T01:19:24Z","title":"维权网 | 黑龙江访民初东方逃脱地方监控继续北京上访（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）黑龙江省佳木斯维权访民初东芳，因其哥哥初少才在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>劝架而被卷入到一起刑事案件中，被判无期徒刑。初东芳为此上访告状，被治安拘留无数次，曾被以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>妨害公务罪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>判处有期徒刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>初东芳出狱后继续为哥哥上访维权。各个信访窗口互相推诿，根本不解决问题。初东芳在多年上访无果的情况下，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>选择跳楼自杀，和其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>人一起爬上北京天安门西侧的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>层楼，以此抗议司法腐败。当日被北京警方以“寻衅滋事罪”刑事拘留，羁押在西城区看守所。初东芳在看守所里绝食抗争被强行灌食。在被羁押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>天后以取保候审的方式被当地政府带回。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>初东芳说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>“哥哥案件的讯问笔录都是伪造的（有字迹鉴定书证实），案件定罪没有物证。公检法采信伪证判哥哥初少才无期徒刑。因此我对本案不服上访维权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>，我拿着鉴定结果证明哥哥初少才的讯问笔录非本人签字时，却遭打击报复。被以“妨害公务罪”判刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>年”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>现在初东芳逃离地方政府的监控，返回北京继续维权。她说：“只要我活着一天，就一定会维权到底！”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_sn6h2F1Q1U/Ue8pxHv2GkI/AAAAAAAAltg/wjQpBWY9Lyc/s1600/2013-07-19+12.42.32.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_sn6h2F1Q1U/Ue8pxHv2GkI/AAAAAAAAltg/wjQpBWY9Lyc/s320/2013-07-19+12.42.32.jpg\" width=\"253\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}